  <content>{"copy":"&lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor8\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: 400px; background-image:url('https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/0be5efd8-21a2-404f-8a8f-14e056079648/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; color: white; align-items: center;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-8 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 40px;\"&gt; &lt;h1&gt;Empower Your Community&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;Join our nonprofit training programs designed to enhance skills and foster growth among community learners and trainers. Enroll now to secure your spot in upcoming sessions.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;button class=\"button1\" onclick=\"window.location.href='#enrollment-info'\"&gt;Explore Enrollment&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-6 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;h2&gt;Why Choose Our Workshops?&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;Our workshops are tailored to meet the needs of diverse community members, providing practical knowledge and hands-on experience. Trainers are experienced professionals passionate about community development.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;button class=\"button1\" onclick=\"window.location.href='#workshop-list'\"&gt;View Workshops&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-6 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;\" alt=\"Community members attending a workshop\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/2c49863f-c788-4b8a-8071-b5b8bcc44855/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;\" alt=\"Participant filling enrollment form\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/506c17f7-e57b-4e82-85d7-a58725bb2573/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Easy Enrollment&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;Submit your details and session preferences quickly and securely. Our streamlined process ensures you get timely updates and confirmation.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;\" alt=\"Trainer guiding community learners\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/b63d3162-f0f6-4502-bcd6-eaa7e5731c62/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Expert Trainers&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;Learn from skilled trainers who bring real-world experience and a passion for empowering communities through education and skill-building.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;\" alt=\"Community members collaborating in workshop\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/c4fe74df-261b-42dd-a5bc-21e07afd1539/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Community Focus&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;Our programs foster collaboration and networking among participants, building a strong foundation for ongoing community growth and support.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\" id=\"enrollment-info\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-12 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;h2&gt;How to Enroll&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;To enroll, please prepare your participant details including contact information and preferred workshop sessions. Our team will assist you through the enrollment process and ensure your preferences are recorded accurately.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;button class=\"button1\" onclick=\"window.location.href='/enrollment'\"&gt;Start Enrollment&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;","enablerating":false,"enabletracking":false,"excludefromsearch":false,"hiddenfromsitemap":false,"sharedpageconfiguration":false,"isroot":false,"rootwebpageid":"6976bca1-d22c-439d-96dd-4399e37c3c91","pagetemplateid":"ab186c9d-1f56-4663-a166-c12fb392dd27","partialurl":"enrollment","publishingstateid":"18c9ace9-f280-41b6-897e-0b274144316b","parentpageid":"52fe0cd3-82e7-4784-a468-ccfd4b17ef00"}</content>
